%pyspark
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dnt2dt

main_spdf = nt.join(uv, ['date', 'time'])\
              .withColumn('datetime', udf_dnt2dt('date', 'time'))\
              .join(sz, 'datetime').drop('date', 'time').sort('datetime')
main_spdf.show()

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType

udf_scaler = udf(lambda s: s / 10000, DoubleType())
ds = main_spdf.select('datetime', 'illum', 'uvi', 'solar_zenith')\
              .withColumn('illum_scaled', udf_scaler('illum'))
ds.show()

%pyspark
import numpy as np
spdf_train_b, spdf_test = ds.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)
spdf_train, spdf_val = spdf_train_b.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)

pdf_train = spdf_train.toPandas()
pdf_val = spdf_val.toPandas()
pdf_test = spdf_test.toPandas()

x_train = np.array(pdf_train[['illum_scaled', 'solar_zenith']])
y_train = np.array(pdf_train['uvi'])

x_val = np.array(pdf_val[['illum_scaled', 'solar_zenith']])
y_val = np.array(pdf_val['uvi'])

x_test = np.array(pdf_test[['illum_scaled', 'solar_zenith']])
y_test = np.array(pdf_test['uvi'])

print('x_train:', len(x_train), 'x_val:', len(x_val), 'x_test:', len(x_test))
print('y_train:', len(y_train), 'y_val:', len(y_val), 'y_test:', len(y_test))

%pyspark
from keras.models import Sequential
from keras.layers import Dense
from keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping

epochs = 500
batch_size = 128

model = Sequential()
model.add(Dense(10, input_dim=2, activation='relu'))
model.add(Dense(20, activation='relu'))
model.add(Dense(1))

model.compile(optimizer='rmsprop', loss='mae', metrics=['mse'])

early_stopping = EarlyStopping(patience=20)

model.fit(x_train, y_train, epochs=epochs, batch_size=batch_size,
          validation_data=(x_val, y_val),
          callbacks=[early_stopping])

%pyspark
loss = model.evaluate(x_test, y_test, batch_size=int(batch_size/2))
print('loss:', str(loss))
